(1, 3965, '', 1, -1, '5 a 7', '17:00:00', '19:00:00', 0, '2016-06-02', '2016-06-02', 'Sorry for the delayed email about this month''s 5 a 7. If you''re ever\r\nwondering when 5 a 7 will be it will usually be the first Thursday of the\r\nmonth.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nIn celebration of summer arriving we will have this 5 a 7 outside in the\r\npark across the street. Feel free to bring a soccer ball, hacky sac, picnic\r\nblanket or other park type equipment. There will also be the oh-so-popular\r\ngames of Concept, Janga and cards set up on blankets and/or tables.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWe''ll have all the food and drinks at the park for 5pm. For those who enjoy\r\nalcoholic beverages please only drink out of plastic cup to allow for\r\ndiscreet consumption J\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nPlease note that this is weather dependent. If it rains we''ll party in the\r\nMullet Room.', 0, NULL, '17:00:00', NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'a:0:{}', '2016-05-31 11:36:12', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0),
(2, 3967, 'june-5a7', 1, 1, 'June 5a7', '17:00:00', '19:00:00', 0, '2016-06-02', '2016-06-02', 'Sorry for the delayed email about this month''s 5 a 7. If you''re ever\r\nwondering when 5 a 7 will be it will usually be the first Thursday of the\r\nmonth.\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-3975 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/IMG_0494-300x225.jpg" alt="IMG_0494" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\nIn celebration of summer arriving we will have this 5 a 7 outside in the\r\npark across the street. Feel free to bring a soccer ball, hacky sac, picnic\r\nblanket or other park type equipment. There will also be the oh-so-popular\r\ngames of Concept, Janga and cards set up on blankets and/or tables.\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-3977 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/soccer-300x202.jpg" alt="soccer" width="300" height="202" />\r\n\r\nWe''ll have all the food and drinks at the park for 5pm. For those who enjoy\r\nalcoholic beverages please only drink out of plastic cup to allow for\r\ndiscreet consumption J\r\n\r\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-3974 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/4672453_orig-300x225.jpg" alt="4672453_orig" width="300" height="225" />\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">Please note that this is weather dependent. If it rains we''ll party in the</span></strong>\r\n<strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">Mullet Room.</span></strong>', 0, NULL, '00:00:00', NULL, 0, 0, 3, NULL, NULL, 'a:0:{}', '2016-05-31 12:47:20', '2016-05-31 16:56:25', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0),
