(3740, 1, '2016-05-19 11:57:37', '2016-05-19 15:57:37', '[vc_row css=".vc_custom_1464812283728{background-image: url(http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/header-what-we-do-75.jpg?id=4114) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1464804826545{padding-top: 10px !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1464815300446{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">KLF Media - Company Values</span></h1>\r\n<div class="content-slider">\r\n<div class="slider">\r\n<div class="mask">\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li class="anim1">\r\n<div class="quote">1. Exceptional customer Service.</div>\r\n<div class="source">Customer service is not a department, it''s an attitude. Always be impeccable in all customer communications, they are why we exist.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim2">\r\n<div class="quote">2. Overachieve.</div>\r\n<div class="source">Set goals in every project and work hard to surpass them. You will feel empowered by your success.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim3">\r\n<div class="quote">3. Disrupt Standards.</div>\r\n<div class="source">Just because its old, doesn''t make it a "classic". Stay curious and educate yourself in notice opportunities and implement change.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim4">\r\n<div class="quote">4. Embrace differences.</div>\r\n<div class="source">Be yourself and embrace the differences in others. Appreciate uniqueness and respect what lies outside of your comfort zone.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim5">\r\n<div class="quote">5. Trust yourself.</div>\r\n<div class="source">Trust that there is always a safety net and nothing can''t be undone, trust your colleagues and their abilities, but mostly trust your knowledge and your intuition; success will follow.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim6">\r\n<div class="quote">6. Create an impact in everything you do.</div>\r\n<div class="source">Always act as if what you are doing makes a difference. Because it does.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim7">\r\n<div class="quote">7. Build true relationships through open communication.</div>\r\n<div class="source">7. Build true relationships through open communication. We are a family, we are a team. Open communication is essential to maintaining our unity.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim8">\r\n<div class="quote">8. Share your knowledge and your passion.</div>\r\n<div class="source">We all have something to share. Never hold back on sharing your knowledge with your peers and always be open to learning from them in return.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim9">\r\n<div class="quote">9. Create happiness around you.</div>\r\n<div class="source">KLF stands for "Keeping Life Fun". Believe in the power of positivity and always remember to smile!</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim10">\r\n<div class="quote">10. There is no 10.</div>\r\n<div class="source">Why? Because we''re not trying to be like everyone else, we''re weird like that!</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap="10"][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1464700576261{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][gears_bp_activity_stream][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1464700592525{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">QUESTIONS</span> <span style="color: #000000;">FEATURE</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n[dwqa-list-questions-homepage][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1465246403269{background-color: #ffffff !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][vc_column