s="source">Always act as if what you are doing makes a difference. Because it does.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim7">\r\n<div class="quote">7. Build true relationships through open communication.</div>\r\n<div class="source">7. Build true relationships through open communication. We are a family, we are a team. Open communication is essential to maintaining our unity.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim8">\r\n<div class="quote">8. Share your knowledge and your passion.</div>\r\n<div class="source">We all have something to share. Never hold back on sharing your knowledge with your peers and always be open to learning from them in return.</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim9">\r\n<div class="quote">9. Create happiness around you.</div>\r\n<div class="source">KLF stands for "Keeping Life Fun". Believe in the power of positivity and always remember to smile!</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="anim10">\r\n<div class="quote">10. There is no 10.</div>\r\n<div class="source">Why? Because we''re not trying to be like everyone else, we''re weird like that!</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap="10"][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1464700576261{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][gears_bp_activity_stream][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1464700592525{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #000000;">QUESTIONS</span> <span style="color: #000000;">FEATURE</span></span></strong></h2>\r\n[dwqa-list-questions-homepage][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1464274934370{background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-